description:
# Last.FM

 Last.FM Rich Presence pulled from the Last.FM API (for now playing). 
 If your music app supports Last.FM, but not discord RPC, you can use this.

For Apple Music mobile, this app can be combined with Eavescrob for a RPC

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Kief5555/EnmityPlugins/master/Last.Fm/build/Last.FM.js
Source: https://github.com/Kief5555/EnmityPlugins/tree/master/Last.Fm/src
